<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section id="faq" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">Find answers to common questions about RizeUp</p>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                        How does the AI resume builder work?
                        <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq1" class="collapse show faq-body">
                        <p>Our AI analyzes your input about your work experience, education, and skills, then generates a professionally formatted resume tailored to your target job. It uses industry best practices and optimization techniques to ensure your resume gets noticed.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                        Is my data secure with RizeUp?
                        <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq2" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Absolutely. We use enterprise-grade security measures to protect your data. Your information is encrypted and never shared with third parties without your consent. You can delete your data at any time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                        Can I try before I subscribe?
                        <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq3" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>Yes! Our free plan allows you to create one complete resume and basic portfolio. You can upgrade to a paid plan anytime to unlock more features and unlimited creations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                        How often is the AI updated?
                        <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq4" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>We continuously update our AI models to reflect the latest hiring trends, resume best practices, and industry standards. Our system learns from thousands of successful resumes to provide you with the best possible results.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-header collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                        What if I need help with my resume?
                        <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div id="faq5" class="collapse faq-body">
                        <p>All users have access to our help center with detailed guides. Professional and Enterprise plan members get priority support and can request one-on-one consultations with our career experts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
